                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2657" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0138</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8401 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">H保险公司“崎岖”的改革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Bumpy road of H company’s Service Reform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">楼园，陈旭</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">H财产保险有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">保险；理赔；服务管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Insurance; Claim; Service management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自2002年以来，随着中国加入世界贸易组织，国有保险公司改革得以全面展开，因此中国保险业得以迅速发展。但值得一提的是，保险市场的规模并没有因保险企业的增多而扩张，因此行业内竞争十分激烈。大多数保险公司在经营上缺乏创新、墨守成规，相互抄袭产品，抢夺渠道的同时大打价格战，恶意竞争的情况屡见不鲜。在此情形下，大多数财产保险公司在反思后决定以提高服务来重新塑造核心竞争力，H保险公司便是其中之一。H公司高层决定对其理赔服务进行一系列的改革，建立专业化的理赔团队，从而可以提高人均产能，降低运营成本，缩短服务周期，最终提高客户满意度，也期待可以通过新的服务模式和举措来吸引更多的消费者。经过周密的计划和安排，H公司正式于2013年启动服务改革计划，其中包括组织架构的调整、制度的变更、人员的整编以及配套IT系统的重建和开发。但是，H公司全新打造的理赔服务不但没有达到预期的效果，反而暴露出一系列新的管理问题。面对改革的首战失利，H公司在公司内部及外部均面临着较大的压力，管理团队需要在短时间内发现项目实施过程中存在的问题，并给予妥善的解决。本文通过案例研究的形式，以H公司对理赔服务的改革为案例，介绍并描述了改革后的H公司在服务管理方面出现的问题。本案例的研究对象是一家民营保险企业，其经营和运营模式在市场上具有一定的代表性。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since 2002, with China&#39;s accession to the World Trade Organization, the reform of domestic insurance companies has been fully developed, so the Chinese insurance industry has been developing rapidly. But it is worth mentioning that the size of the insurance market is not expanded with the increasing number of insurance companies and expansion, so the competition is very fierce in the industry. There is no doubt that the most of domestic insurance companies are all lack of innovation, they copy other&#39;s products , snatch distribution channels while having price war against each other, in a word, the malicious competition is nothing new. In this case, most of the property insurance companies reflect upon the decision to improve service to rebuild the core competitiveness, H property insurance company is one of them. Therefore, H company&#39;s senior executives decided to rebuild their claim services, by creating Professional service team, accordingly, they aim to improve the production capacity , lower the operation costs at the same time. Most importantly, improving customer satisfaction is also expected. H Company initiated the revolution plan in 2013, which included several adjustments from organizational structure to IT system upgrading. Unfortunately, the whole plan was failed to meet the requirements, besides, lots of management problems were exposed as result. H Company has to confront and suffer from stress internally and externally. Apparently, they need to fix those problems as soon as possible. In this paper, in the form of case studies to H&#39;s reform claims service as a case, combining services management, theory and methods of operation and management, presentation and described reformed H companies with personnel management, service capacity and service innovation problems, and to analyze and assess these issues. The research object of this case is a private insurance company; its business model in the market has certain representativeness. At the same time the conclusions and recommendations of this case study could also be a useful reference to the similar enterprises service reform.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》、《服务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">运营流程再造；服务创新；服务补救；服务质量</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-04</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
